resources.string: Welcome to my current Euler Solutions. Please select a problem from the list.
Given a maximum value and two multiples, find the sum of the all of the multiples.
For example, consider a max value of 17 and the multiples 3 and 4. The multiples of 3 and 4 less than 17 are 3, 4, 6, 8, 9, 12, 15, and 16. Their sum is 73.
